dern wird.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 4aDemografischer Wandel. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aPolitik. 4aRaum. 4aRecht. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 4aSozialgeographie. 4aSoziologie. 4aStadt. 4aTerritoriale Ungleichheit. 4aUrban Studies. 4aZusammenhalt. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aCity.  aCultural Studies.  aDemographic Change.  aLaw.  aPolitics.  aSocial Geography.  aSocial Inequality.  aSociety.  aSociology.  aSpace.  aTerritorial Inequality.  aUrban Studies.1 aNeu, Claudia, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aVogel, Berthold, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology 2022z9783110994520oZDB-23-DSL0 cprintz978383765752440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839457528?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839457528423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839457528/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DSLb2022